dcMetadata.abstract_tsi: Details northern coasts of Newfoundland and the Saint Lawrence River as far west as Anticosti Island. Continued by a separate untitled chart, drawn at a reduced scale, covering the river west to the city of Quebec (Ayer MS map 218). Includes many Indian place names.
